data.description: Incredible opportunity to purchase almost 2.5 acres in the gentrifying South Mountain area. Zoned Multi-Family R-3, this property has 3 structures on it. First, there is a charming older home which can be remodeled. Second, there is a double wide trailer built in 2003. Third, there is a metal shed. Drive down Desert Ln and you're surrounded multiple million dollar properties and desert landscape just minutes from incredible hiking, biking, and horse trails. Property can be split! Turn the land into a horse property or use it as an investment opportunity to earn income. Easy access to Sky Harbor, ASU, i-10. Owned by the same family for almost 30 years!
